<FACE_ALLEN><POS_RIGHT><FACE_LOSS>
Hmm? <MYNAME>, you don't look so well.

<FACE_ALLEN><POS_RIGHT><FACE_LOSS>
What's wrong, <MYNAME>? Hang in there!

<FACE_ALLEN><POS_LEFT><FACE_SAD>
Dr. Klaus, tell me quickly! What's going
on with <MYNAME>? Some sort of disease?

<FACE_KUROZE><POS_RIGHT><FACE_PATI>
What is this nonsense you talk about?
There is absolutely nothing wrong with
her, or with her baby.

<FACE_KUROZE><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
You are pregnant. You two are going to
be parents! Congratulations!

<FACE_ALLEN><POS_LEFT><FACE_ROUGH>
What? A child! Well done, <MYNAME>. Allow
me to praise you.

<FACE_KUROZE><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
It is natural to rejoice, but there are
several matters that you must treat with
utmost care during early pregnancy.
<PAGE>
Do not strain yourself until everything
is stable. Rest as often as possible.
Allen, you must care diligently for her.

<FACE_ALLEN><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
How are you feeling, my princess?
Please, rest whenever you feel like it.

<FACE_ALLEN><POS_RIGHT><FACE_LOVE>
You really know how to make me happy, my
princess! I am truly grateful for this.
Thank you, <MYNAME>!

<FACE_ROD><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>
<MYNAME>, are you feeling all right? You
look a bit ill. Maybe you should lie
down for a moment...

<FACE_ROD><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>
<MYNAME>!! Th... this is serious! I have
to take you quickly to Dr. Klaus!

<FACE_ROD><POS_LEFT><FACE_SAD>
Dr. Klaus, is <MYNAME> okay? Could it be
some awful disease?

<FACE_ROD><POS_LEFT><FACE_ROUGH>
Woohoo! <MYNAME>, did you hear that? We're
having a baby!!

<FACE_KUROZE><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
It is natural to rejoice, but there are
several matters that you must treat with
utmost care during early pregnancy.
<PAGE>
Do not strain yourself until everything
is stable. Rest as often as possible.
Rod, you must care diligently for her.

<FACE_ROD><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
<MYNAME>, how have you been feeling? Any
better than before?

<FACE_ROD><POS_RIGHT><FACE_LOVE>
I'm so happy you are pregnant! So this
is how it feels to become a father...
I couldn't be any more excited!
<PAGE>
Thank you, <MYNAME>. I love you.

<FACE_SENGOKU><POS_RIGHT><FACE_LOSS>
Hmmm? <MYNAME>, dear, is there something
wrong? You look pale...

<FACE_SENGOKU><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ANGRY>
<MYNAME>!! I'm taking you to see Dr. Klaus
immediately. Please be strong!

<FACE_SENGOKU><POS_LEFT><FACE_LOSS>
So, what do you say, Dr. Klaus? Is
<MYNAME> very sick? Oh, I don't even want
to think about that!

<FACE_SENGOKU><POS_LEFT><FACE_LOVE>
I'm becoming a father? This news got me
more surprised than any scoop! I'm at
a loss! How should I react?
<PAGE>
<FACE_ROUGH>My dear <MYNAME>, bravo! You are simply
amazing! I am over the moon!

<FACE_KUROZE><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
It is natural to rejoice, but there are
several matters that you must treat with
utmost care during early pregnancy.
<PAGE>
Do not strain yourself until everything
is stable. Rest as often as possible.
Soseki, care diligently for her.

<FACE_SENGOKU><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
My dear <MYNAME>, how do you feel? Don't
hesitate to tell me about the slightest
change, yes?

<FACE_SENGOKU><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
I wish I could lessen your pain... but
other than that, just say the word and
I'll do whatever you need.
<PAGE>
I hope you love this baby and me dearly,
my lovely <MYNAME>! This child is the
supreme symbol of our love.

<FACE_SERUKA><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>
My dearest <MYNAME>, what seems to be the
matter? You don't look your best.

<FACE_SERUKA><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>
Dearest <MYNAME>, are you all right!?
Please stay strong!

<FACE_SERUKA><POS_LEFT><FACE_SAD>
Please tell me, Dr. Klaus, what is the
reason behind <MYNAME>'s indisposition?
<PAGE>
I sincerely hope she's not ill...

<FACE_SERUKA><POS_LEFT><FACE_PATI>
...
<PAGE>
<FACE_LOVE>I apologize. My overwhelming happiness
must have gotten in the way of my words.

<FACE_KUROZE><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
It is natural to rejoice, but there are
several matters that you must treat with
utmost care during early pregnancy.
<PAGE>
Do not strain yourself until everything
is stable. Rest as often as possible.
Sanjay, care diligently for her.

<FACE_SERUKA><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
Dearest, <MYNAME>, do you feel any
discomfort? Please let me know if you
need something.

<FACE_SERUKA><POS_RIGHT><FACE_LOVE>
I never dreamt this day would come, just
like the day I married you. I can't
measure the happiness I'm feeling now.
<PAGE>
<MYNAME>, dear, I deeply appreciate you
building a family with me. May our child
be very healthy.

<FACE_NEEL><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
What's wrong, <MYNAME>? You look terrible!

<FACE_NEEL><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ANGRY>
Oh no! Hang in there, <MYNAME>! <MYNAME>!

<FACE_NEEL><POS_LEFT><FACE_SAD>
What the heck just happened, Dr. Klaus?
What's wrong with <MYNAME>? Don't tell me
her life is at risk!

<FACE_NEEL><POS_LEFT><FACE_LOVE>
Wow, I'm astonished... we're having...
a kid? My hands are shaking from this
news!

<FACE_KUROZE><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
It is natural to rejoice, but there are
several matters that you must treat with
utmost care during early pregnancy.
<PAGE>
Do not strain yourself until everything
is stable. Rest as often as possible.
Neil, you must care diligently for her.

<FACE_NEEL><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
Uhm... how... how are you feeling? Don't
hold anything back, just tell me!

<FACE_NEEL><POS_RIGHT><FACE_LOVE>
<MYNAME>, I'm so thrilled with your
pregnancy! And happy, too, of course!
I must work even harder from now on.

<FACE_SYUMITTO><POS_RIGHT><FACE_LOSS>
My lovely <MYNAME>, is something wrong?
Do you want to lie down on our bed?

<FACE_SYUMITTO><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ANGRY>
No! Please hang in there, <MYNAME>! I'm
taking you to the hospital right now.

<FACE_SYUMITTO><POS_LEFT><FACE_LOSS>
Dr. Klaus, did <MYNAME>'s situation get
any worse? She seems to be in a lot of
pain...

<FACE_SYUMITTO><POS_LEFT><FACE_ROUGH>
My child? Is that right? <MYNAME>, thank
you so much! There's no describing my
joy at this moment!

<FACE_KUROZE><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
It is natural to rejoice, but there are
several matters that you must treat with
utmost care during early pregnancy.
<PAGE>
Do not strain yourself until everything
is stable. Rest as often as possible.
Amir, you must care diligently for her.

<FACE_SYUMITTO><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
<MYNAME>, my dear, how do you feel? As a
man, I don't really understand what you
are going through...
<PAGE>
<MYNAME>, since you always work so hard,
please allow yourself to rest, at least
during your pregnancy.

<FACE_SYUMITTO><POS_RIGHT><FACE_LOVE>
I will definitely never forget this day!
Thank you, <MYNAME>. I love you more than
words can say.

<FACE_TINA><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>
<MYNAME>, help me. I feel awful... and I
think I might... throw up.

This looks serious! Let's hurry to the
hospital.

<FACE_TINA><POS_LEFT><FACE_SAD>
Dr. Klaus, what is happening to me? Is
it some terrible sickness？

<FACE_TINA><POS_LEFT><FACE_LOSS>
Whaaaaaat!? I... I would have never
imagined this!
<PAGE>
<FACE_LOVE>There's a baby inside of me...
Heeheehee... I'm so happy! <RED>∀</RED>

<FACE_KUROZE><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
It is natural to rejoice, but there are
several matters that you must treat with
utmost care during early pregnancy.
<PAGE>
Do not strain yourself until everything
is stable. Rest as often as possible.
<PAGE>
<MYNAME>, you should stay alert to the
slightest changes on her health.

<FACE_TINA><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
Okay. I feel much better than a while
ago. Thank you for bringing me to the
hospital!

<FACE_TINA><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
Actually, I think this surprise just
blew my nausea away!
<PAGE>
<FACE_LOVE>It still feels like a dream, but this
happiness is 100% real! <RED>∀</RED> <MYNAME>,
please take good care of us!

<FACE_MICHEL><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>
Something is off with me today. I have
never felt quite like this! I feel like
I could faint at any moment.

This looks serious! Let's hurry to the
hospital.

<FACE_MICHEL><POS_LEFT><FACE_SAD>
Dr. Klaus, what's going on with my body?
Is it some terrible illness? If so,
please tell me you can heal it!

<FACE_MICHEL><POS_LEFT><FACE_ROUGH>
Wow... <RED>∀</RED> Do you really mean it, Dr.
Klaus!?
<PAGE>
So, what now, <MYNAME>? I'm so happy, I
can't think straight anymore!

<FACE_MICHEL><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ANGRY>
Aahh, now I'm really tired. It takes a
lot of effort to keep looking this cute
when you're not feeling well.
<PAGE>
<MYNAME>, I hope you'll take even better
care of me from now on.

<FACE_MICHEL><POS_RIGHT><FACE_LOVE>
Maybe it's a bit early to have a child,
but I think the baby will be more
pleased to have a young, cute mother!
<PAGE>
I'm looking forward to it, too. In any
case, I should rest for a while.

<FACE_YURI><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>
<MYNAME>... I'm in pain... please help
me...

This looks serious! Let's hurry to the
hospital.

<FACE_YURI><POS_LEFT><FACE_SAD>
Dr. Klaus... am I... terribly sick?

<FACE_YURI><POS_LEFT><FACE_LOVE>
I am... so content! My mother... will be
euphoric!

<FACE_YURI><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
I feel... much better, now. Thank you!
I must... must give my mother this great
news.

<FACE_YURI><POS_RIGHT><FACE_LOVE>
I always wanted to have a child. That's
why... I'm so excited. <MYNAME>, I love
you! <RED>∀</RED>

<FACE_IROHA><POS_RIGHT><FACE_LOSS>
<MYNAME>, please come and help me... I
feel so bad, I...

This looks serious! Let's hurry to the
hospital.

<FACE_IROHA><POS_LEFT><FACE_LOSS>
Dr. Klaus, what is happening to me?
Please, don't tell me it's a dreadful
illness!

<FACE_IROHA><POS_LEFT><FACE_LOVE>
A ch... a child? I have always wanted
one, but I didn't think my wish would
come true so fast!

<FACE_IROHA><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
Yes, I feel better now. My pain is
almost completely gone.
<PAGE>
I'm sorry to have worried you. Thank you
for taking such good care of me.

<FACE_IROHA><POS_RIGHT><FACE_LOVE>
Proposal, marriage, pregnancy... there
are so many great things going on in my
life right now, it's almost scary! 
<PAGE>
Nevertheless, I am glad that you are
delighted by the news, too, <MYNAME>. That
is what matters the most to me.
<PAGE>
I might give you some trouble from now
on, but... I'm counting on you, Daddy.

<FACE_FELICIA><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>
<MYNAME>... what should we do? I feel
nauseous, and it's getting worse by
the minute...

This looks serious! Let's hurry to the
hospital.

<FACE_FELICIA><POS_LEFT><FACE_LOSS>
Dr. Klaus, is everything okay with my
body？
<PAGE>
Perhaps I'm feeling sick because I've
been eating too much...

<FACE_FELICIA><POS_LEFT><FACE_LOSS>
...am I dreaming?
<PAGE>
<FACE_LOVE>...pinching my cheek doesn't work. So it
must be true!

<FACE_FELICIA><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
<MYNAME>, pumpkin, thank you so much for 
bringing me to the hospital!
<PAGE>
I won't be able to eat much for a while,
but no sacrifice is too big for the
baby!

<FACE_FELICIA><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
Daddy and Mommy... it sounds lovely,
doesn't it? I feel like I'm about to
melt from too much joy! <RED>∀</RED>

<FACE_WITCH><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>
<MYNAME>, sweetie pie. I don't feel as 
terrific as usual... do you think we 
have some medicine?

This looks serious! Let's hurry to the
hospital.

<FACE_WITCH><POS_LEFT><FACE_LOSS>
What could possibly be happening? Maybe
some lackey from that wretched Goddess
cast a terrible spell on me!

<FACE_WITCH><POS_LEFT><FACE_LOVE>
My, oh my! What a surprise. <MYNAME>, I
hope you appreciate this news!

<FACE_WITCH><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
I'm bewildered that a child can be born
from the union of a human and a witch!
But you look delighted, <MYNAME>.

<FACE_WITCH><POS_RIGHT><FACE_LOVE>
I think I can put up with this, seeing
it make you so happy. I'll be counting
on you, <MYNAME>!
Allen
Rod
Soseki
Sanjay
Neil
Amir
Tina
Michelle
Yuri
Iroha
Felicity
Witch Princess
